  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl59_LabelType\">You cast no shadow whatsoever, or the shadow you do have is monstrous. Under normal lighted conditions, this is not hard to observe&mdash;but uncommon to notice.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Effects</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl59_LabelType\">Creatures that succeed at a DC 15 Wisdom check notice it plainly (an additional Perception check may be required based on environmental conditions). This telltale sign of wickedness cannot be concealed by <em>misdirection</em>, <em>nondetection</em>, or illusions, except those that also affect shadows (such as <em>invisibility</em>).<br /></span></p>",
